{"tid":622104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【淺層地震】日本島根6.1級地震 3傷建築物受損","createTime":"2018-04-09T00:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T00:49:19.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8b99300a3369a80308ae0a39d605ea5a85025069","tid":622104,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:49:19.000Z","msg":"香港樓市已死亡 !<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180409/58049954\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180409%2F58049954&d=DnGt14bLslLs%2Bf4urVGPoV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=cda38a29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180409%2F58049954&h=780c065a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180409/58049954</a><br />\n<br />\n日本西部島根縣周一凌晨發生6.1級淺層地震，3人受輕傷，建築物與道路受損，另有部份家庭停水停電。當局警告，未來幾天可能仍有強震。<br />\n<br />\n日本氣象廳表示，這宗地震當地凌晨1時23分發生，震源深度12公里。美國地質調查所（USGS）錄得強度5.7級。震央在廣島市以北96公里，本州西部都可感受到搖晃。<br />\n共同社報道，有3人受到輕傷，約100戶家庭停水、50戶家庭停電，又說也有一些建築與道路受損。<br />\n附近的島根核能發電廠沒有出現問題。"}]}